brandComInfo.introduce: Zec, Ltd. is an IT company with a professional focus on system integration and technical services. It aims to provide top-tier technical expertise and best-quality services. We provide technical advices concerning customized system integration; professional services for information system construction; and a full set of after-sales technical support and customer training. Solutions of the IDC’s Centralized Management, E-learning System, SAP Basis technical support, and Network Security services are included. In addition, we provide software consultation in related areas, primarily including application system developing on common programming languages and platforms, as well as Software Quality Assurance. Our professional service can effectively shorten project development cycle, cut investment and improve the reliability, stability, security and performance of the project in proper, in the hope of constructing a best-quality application and software system for the customers.
